snippet.description:

or

-------------------------------------------------------------- 
  
Welcome to Day 1 of the 2025 PUBG MOBILE National Championship South Asia Fall Grand Finals.
From 15th to 17th August, the Top 16 teams from the Playoffs will compete in a three-day showdown, playing 5 matches per day starting at 18:00 GMT +5:45.
The finalists will share a $10,000 prize pool, but only the Top 2 teams will secure seeding slots for the 2025 PMSL CSA Fall. One Dream, One Victory.

While the best teams fight in the PMNC Grand Finals, your journey can start now!
Sign up for the PUBG MOBILE Nepal Series (PMNS) S3 and take your first step to the big stage.
PMNS REGISTRATION LINK : https://forms.gle/As3cL3pytbxK7aWu5

Grand Finals Schedule

snippet.title: Bipul Chettri - Eh Saathi (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
'Eh Saathi' is the first release from the forthcoming album, 'Pravah'. As the title suggests, it's an ode to childhood friendships that transcends time. Almost written like a conversation piece put to music, the song embodies the notion of friendship that is something to nurture and celebrate, that you never take them for granted and its enduring nature of emphasizing loyalty, love, and the shared journey of life.

MUSIC
Bipul Chettri - Vocals, Guitars, Backing Vocals 
Pranai Gurung - Guitars
Rahul Rai - Bass
Rythem Bansal - Keys/Organ
Shantanu Sudarshan - Drums/Percussions 
Sumimardor Diengdoh, Bhushan Man Amatya, Prashansa Pandey Amatya - Backing Vocals 

Written and arranged by Bipul Chettri.
Recorded at Baa Baa Black Sheep Studios, Plug ‚ÄòN‚Äô Play Studios & Project Studio Productions.
Recording Engineers - Jonty Indra, Anindo Bose, Binaya Man Amatya 
Mixed & Mastered by Binaya Man Amatya
Album Cover Design - Manohar Rai
Album Cover Photography - Praveen Chettri
Producer - Bipul Chettri
Executive Producer - Sonam Tashi

snippet.title: Minecraft Speedrunning (I'M LIVE AGAIN)
snippet.description:
Minecraft Speedrunning (I'M LIVE AGAIN)

DISCLAIMER: I am CHEATING! (Technically)

I am using mods that are not allowed in official leaderboard speedruns. This is practice for my videos, not for world records! I am also simulating ender eye calculation using a mod, I am only throwing the eyes to simulate a time spend, as official speedrunners use a bot to calculate the stronghold location off of 1/2 ender eyes.

I am also using no fog, optifine zoom, increased pearl rates (matching 1.16 rates), and a custom f3 menu with Nether Coordinates. (And maybe more, idk, who cares)

lava_hunter03 is playing his Minecraft world as normal, but than one day everything changes. He suddenly becomes inactive on all of his accounts, and goes silent. After investigating, we discover some horrifying secrets linked to the player.

This is a series called Minecraft ARG where I solve Minecraft mysteries. Not Secret Minecraft things or Minecraft lore (like Game Theory) or Escape Rooms, but a research based series dedicated to solving Minecraft arg channels. What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It‚Äôs unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX ‚Äî interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything ‚Äî be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer ‚ÄúCapture the Flag‚Äù game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (‚ÄúRobux‚Äù). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

‚ú® Achyutam Keshavam ‚Äì A Devotional Krishna Bhajan ‚ú®
 "Achyutam Keshavam" is a timeless and soul-soothing bhajan dedicated to Lord Krishna, praising their divine names, virtues, and forms. The bhajan beautifully recites various names of the Lord - Achyuta, Keshava, Narayana, and more - each carrying deep spiritual meaning.
Singing this bhajan is believed to purify the heart, remove sorrows, and bring the blessings of the Supreme Lord. It reminds devotees to surrender completely to God, trusting His eternal protection and grace.


üå∏ Chant ‚ÄúAchyutam Keshavam‚Äù with devotion and invite divine bliss into your life.

Credits:
Singer - Saee Tembhekar
Music - Kamlesh Bhadkamkar
Lyrics - Traditional
Chorus - Shripad Lele, Vivek Naik, Unmesh Chandavarkar, Shardul Kavthekar, Seema Lele, Mrunmayi Dadke, Sapna Heman, Dhanashree Kashid
Flute - Varad Kathapurkar
Rhythm - Archis Lele, Hanumant Rawade, Vijay Jadhav, Anil Karanjavkar, Shashank Hadkar, Bharat Bhadkamkar
Guitar - Rahul Deo
Sound Engineer - Shrikrishna Sawant

‚ú® Achyutam Keshavam ‚Äì A Devotional Krishna Bhajan ‚ú®
 "Achyutam Keshavam" is a timeless and soul-soothing bhajan dedicated to Lord Krishna, praising their divine names, virtues, and forms. The bhajan beautifully recites various names of the Lord - Achyuta, Keshava, Narayana, and more - each carrying deep spiritual meaning.
Singing this bhajan is believed to purify the heart, remove sorrows, and bring the blessings of the Supreme Lord. It reminds devotees to surrender completely to God, trusting His eternal protection and grace.


üå∏ Chant ‚ÄúAchyutam Keshavam‚Äù with devotion and invite divine bliss into your life.
